nodes.text: Karhei was a male Chagrian sergeant of the White Maw pirate gang during the Galactic War. After his boss Shai Tenna attempted a failed coup against White Maw Gen'Dai leaders and perished at the hand of the Voidhound, Karhei and other Tenna's men could not return to the White Maw and so set up to work for the smuggler instead.
